# Implement Real-Time Collaboration with Yjs and Tiptap

Use Yjs, integrated with Tiptap via the `y-prosemirror` binding, for real-time collaborative editing features. Manage WebSocket connections efficiently through the custom AWS WebSocket server to synchronize document changes across users, ensuring low latency and reliable updates.

More details in this ADR: [adr-004-real-time-collab.md](mdc:docs/app-design/architecture-decision-records/adr-004-real-time-collab.md).
